2.2 弹幕内容-情感分布饼图¶

In [19]:
# 
def sentiment_analyse(v_cmt_list):

    score_list = []  # 
    tag_list = []  # 
    pos_count = 0  # -
    neg_count = 0  # -
    mid_count = 0  # -
    for comment in v_cmt_list:
        tag = ''
        sentiments_score = SnowNLP(comment).sentiments
        if sentiments_score < 0.5:
            tag = ''
            neg_count += 1
        elif sentiments_score > 0.5:
            tag = ''
            pos_count += 1
        else:
            tag = ''
            mid_count += 1
        score_list.append(sentiments_score)  # 
        tag_list.append(tag)  # 
    df[''] = score_list
    df[''] = tag_list
    grp = df[''].value_counts()
    print('')
    print(grp)
    grp.plot.pie(y='', autopct='%.2f%%')  # 
    plt.title('bBarrage_')
    plt.savefig('bBarrage_.png')  # 
    # excel
    df.to_excel('bBarrage_.xlsx', index=None)
    print('bBarrage_.xlsx')
